  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: a99e728c065cf4800b20910a4b138d52, type: 3}
  m_Name: Level 0 Chat
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  messageContentList:
  - message: 'Welcome. Warm congratulations on your new position as admissions officer
      at <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>Uncommon Academy</b></wave>, the most prestigious
      magical university in Unmeiia, as well as the known world. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: As you may recall from our interview, I will be your supervisor during
      your time here.
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: "Apologies for the quick turnaround, but you\u2019ve been brought on
      board right on the cusp of our first international admission season in <wave
      a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>20 years</b></wave>. It\u2019s a big day."
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: My instructions will have to be brief.
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: dee2c29c0fdf2534fb17fc02f8d72a29, type: 3}
  - message: 'On the left-hand side of the screen, you can see the student portrait,
      name, and base statistics: <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>financial standing</b></wave>,
      and <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>academic aptitude</b></wave>. '
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 9c5132fde94437f4d9d0c314bf9303c8, type: 3}
  - message: "These base statistics will affect our school\u2019s overall <wave a=0.1
      f=1 w=1><b>academic</b></wave> and <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>financial</b></wave>
      performance scores. Keep an eye on how they are weighted. "
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 704adb58ac684b7428e7037df30a40d9, type: 3}
  - message: 'The  <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>scholarship fund</b></wave> situated beneath
      the academic and finance scores is expended whenever a student without a full
      finance bar is admitted to Uncommon Academy. Unless the bar is completely full,
      they will not be able to attend the academy out of pocket. '
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1ff54d188baefa54487e043ca81d043b, type: 3}
  - message: 'Keep an eye on your <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>scholarship fund</b></wave>,
      because it can run out. Students lacking finances <color=#DF5749>cannot</color>
      be accepted when the scholarship fund is depleted. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: To the left of the overall school scores are the student preferences
      and demographics. These pieces of background information will be relevant in
      the future.
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 2518896090bce7141aac78a890f65c71, type: 3}
  - message: For now, just familiarize yourself with where they are located. They
      will be relevant later.
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: 'When you are ready to make a decision, you may select either the <color=#47B34C><bounce
      a=0.1 f=0.5 w=1><b>Admit</b></bounce></color> or <color=#DF5749><bounce a=0.1
      f=0.5 w=1><b>Reject</b></bounce></color> options from the bottom right-hand
      corner. Just click, and the admissions software will take care of the rest. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: If I ever contact you with updates, click on the <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>chat
      icon</b></wave> at the bottom left-hand corner of the screen. To return to
      the admissions page from the chat log, just click on it again to minimize this
      window.
    sprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: f1f6aa68fc8dc9d46aef5d6614e385fd, type: 3}
  - message: "<wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>One last thing\u2026</b></wave>"
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: 'As you already know, and as I reminded you at the beginning of this
      conversation, this is our first international admission season since before
      the war. A conflict spanning nearly 2 decades, leaving no corner of the known
      world untouched. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: 'Keep in mind, as you perform your task, just how momentous of a time
      this is for our institution. I cannot afford to be forgiving of mistakes. '
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
  - message: That is all. <wave a=0.1 f=1 w=1><b>Good luck</b></wave>.
    sprite: {fileID: 0}
